This paper deals with lower bounds for testing properties of Boolean functions, which is a topic in computational complexity theory (cs.CC) and data structures (cs.DS). The techniques used in the paper involve information theory (cs.IT) and probabilistic analysis (cs.LG). Additionally, the study of Boolean functions is closely related to discrete mathematics (cs.DM).
